### Confirm User (Email Validation)
GET http://localhost:8000/users/confirm/{{sample_token}}

### Resend Email Token
GET http://localhost:8000/users/newtoken

### Get Current User Data (requires auth)
GET http://localhost:8000/users/
Authorization: Bearer {{sample_token}}

### Get All Users (admin only)
GET http://localhost:8000/users/all
Authorization: Bearer {{sample_token}}

### Get Only Blocked Users (admin only)
GET http://localhost:8000/users/blocked
Authorization: Bearer {{sample_token}}


