### Reset Password (Request)
POST http://localhost:8000/users/reset/password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@admin.com"
}

### Change Reset Password (With Token)
POST http://localhost:8000/users/reset/password/change
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "reset-token-here",
  "newPassword": "Newpassword123"
}

### Change Password (requires auth)
POST http://localhost:8000/users/change/password
Authorization: Bearer {{sample_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "oldPassword": "currentpassword",
  "newPassword": "newpassword123"
}

### Change Username (requires auth)
POST http://localhost:8000/users/change/username
Authorization: Bearer {{sample_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newUsername": "newusername"
}

